Vave, 

Me and your Acha were not prepared for this moment, we never imagined we’d be blessed with you so soon. You came into our lives as the sweetest surprise, one that changed everything in the best way. From the very second we found out you were growing inside Amma’s womb, we were ready — not just in our minds, but in our hearts and souls.

From that moment, nothing else mattered. Whether you are a girl or a boy, you instantly became njangade vavaa🥹. Every heartbeat, every prayer, every dream since then has been only for you. We can’t wait to meet you, our world already revolves around you. 💛

Love
Amma🥹

A full circle of love. ❤️
